# Web3Forms — relays the contact form to your inbox without a backend.
# Setup (30 seconds):
#   1. Visit https://web3forms.com
#   2. Enter your email: contact@creativegrid.cloud
#   3. Copy the Access Key they send you
#   4. Rename this file to `.env.local` and paste the key below
#   5. Restart `npm run dev`
#
# Until you add a key, the form falls back to opening the user's mail client
# via a pre-filled mailto: link.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
